If theres a nicer drink to have sitting by a fire on a miserable winters day Ive yet to find it. 
beautiful full rich taste.
not really one for ciders, but really tangy and fruity.

crisp, flavourless beer sold as the Premium beer in Australia but in that regard is vastly overrated. 

too expensive to drink in large quantities, and not good enough to really want to.
exported to the world so that Australians dont have to drink it
in my opinion Australias best beer.

real friends wouldnt let their friends drink this stuff. 
truly awful
